Packed layout record Pair has left: u8; right: u8.

To write pair pair: Pair into bytes: buffer of 2 u8.
Write pair into bytes at 0.

To main, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 2 u8 filled with 0.
Let pair be Pair with left be 5 and right be 6.
Write pair pair into bytes.
Give (bytes at 0 as i32) plus (bytes at 1 as i32).
